# Block zip uploads. The v3.3.0 design handoff bundle was uploaded
# directly to main via the GitHub web UI on 2026-05-04 (commits
# 43612f3 → a80163a) and deleted 2 minutes later. The blob is permanent
# in pack history; un-rewriting requires force-pushing all of main and
# wasn't worth it. This rule prevents the next one. NO allowlist entries:
# the previous one (the docs/ WhatsApp export zip) was real client data on a
# public repo and was removed 2026-06-12 (docs/RUNBOOK_REPO_PRIVATE_CUTOVER.md).
*.zip

# Client-data hygiene (2026-06-12): raw client exports and customer estimate
# PDFs must never be committed. The WhatsApp thread export + real customer
# estimates (GST numbers) were git-rm'ed from HEAD on 2026-06-12 — keep them
# out. blueprints_sample/ may only carry the sanitized synthetic example.
WhatsApp Chat*
/docs/WhatsApp*
/blueprints_sample/*
!/blueprints_sample/blueprints_example.pdf

# Fleet-local build secrets for deploy-production-local.sh (never commit)
ops/env/production.build.env

